# Rule 9: Windows Event Log Clearing
# --------------------------------------------------
# Description: Detects the deletion or clearing of Windows Event Logs using 
# wevtutil.exe or PowerShell, typically done by attackers to hide their activities.
# 
# MITRE ATT&CK: T1070.001 (Indicator Removal: Clear Windows Event Logs)
# Severity: Critical
# 
# Logic (Sigma-style):
#   - EventID: 1102 (The audit log was cleared) OR 104 (System log was cleared)
#   - ProcessName: 'wevtutil.exe' AND CommandLine contains 'cl'
#   - PowerShell: 'Clear-EventLog' or 'Remove-EventLog'
# 
# Log Source: Windows Security Log / System Log
